extends ../new/layout_tailwind
block css
block js
block content
    div(class="max-w-7xl mx-auto p-4")
        div(class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg mb-8")
            h2(class="text-center text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-[#332D56] bg-gray-200 py-4 rounded-t-lg")
                | Service & Delivery Policy
            div(class="p-6")
                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 1. Introduction
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | At YDCC Bank, we are committed to delivering reliable and efficient
                        | banking services to all our customers. This policy outlines how we
                        | provide services across our branches and digital platforms while
                        | maintaining transparency and customer satisfaction.

                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 2. Transaction Processing
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | All banking transactions including deposits, withdrawals, fund transfers,
                        | and loan disbursements are processed promptly and securely. Our goal is to
                        | ensure minimal delays and smooth service delivery both at branches and
                        | through online channels.

                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 3. Availability of Services
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | Banking facilities are available during official working hours at our
                        | branches and 24/7 through our mobile banking and digital platforms. We
                        | continuously strive to provide uninterrupted access to essential banking
                        | services.

                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 4. Account & Service Registration
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | Customers can open accounts, apply for loans, and register for digital
                        | banking services with ease. Once registered, they can enjoy seamless
                        | access to a variety of cooperative banking facilities.

                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 5. Customer Support
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | Our dedicated support team is available to assist with queries related to
                        | accounts, transactions, loans, or digital banking services. Customers are
                        | encouraged to contact us through our branch network, helplines, or official
                        | communication channels.

                div(class="mb-6")
                    h3(class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#4E6688]") 6. Regular Updates
                    p(class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed")
                        | We regularly update our services, technology, and policies to align with
                        | regulatory requirements and modern banking practices. Customers are kept
                        | informed about important updates through official notices, our website,
                        | and mobile app.

                p(class="text-sm md:text-base text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4")
                    | Thank you for banking with YDCC Bank. If you have any questions or require
                    | further assistance, please reach out to our customer support team. We look
                    | forward to serving your financial needs with trust and dedication.
